Red Velvet best MVs in my opinion :
1.Bad Boy
Damn gurl, this concept, outfit, dance, and everything are on point, timeless and still such a bop
2. Automatic
This is underrated but such a BOP! the MV giving me 80s music video style with such a very sexy concept, i just love it sooo much! the song is really addicting for me
3. Psycho
Queenssss oh my Gooodd!! the comeback never dissapoint me, their visuals, vocal and everything especially their outfits are just on point, it is so catchy, sexy and beautiful they are really queens of concept!
4. Russian Roulette
The MV is just so simple, cute and girl crush vibe. Red Velvet never dissapoint me, the psycho vibe giving me chills and really addicting.. so natural and overall cute
